==個人生活==
鄭志雯是香港富商[[鄭家純_(香港企業家)|鄭家純]]之長女<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://info.meadin.com/BrandDynamics/2010-12-21/1012215265.shtml |title=女掌门人郑志雯：11亿美元拓新世界酒店 |accessdate=2011-06-01 |archive-date=2012-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120612044231/http://info.meadin.com/BrandDynamics/2010-12-21/1012215265.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，家族成員包括[[鄭志剛|鄭志剛]]、[[鄭志明|鄭志明]]和鄭志亮。其丈夫是「鋼鐵大王」龐鼎元孫兒龐建貽<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbesasia/2017/07/26/next-tycoon-sonia-cheng-and-husband-paulo-pong-kin-yee-share-an-interest-in-business/#5212808b7b3d|title=Rosewood's Sonia Cheng and Husband Paulo Pong Kin-Yee Share An Interest In Business|date=2017-07-26|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|access-date=12020-03-11|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405070541/https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbesasia/2017/07/26/next-tycoon-sonia-cheng-and-husband-paulo-pong-kin-yee-share-an-interest-in-business/#5212808b7b3d|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鄭志雯熱心教育及公益事務，積極推動及參與[[新世界集團|新世界集團]]於香港及內地的多項公益項目<ref>{{cite web |title=【支援醫護】新世界集團旗下酒店將為前線醫護提供免費住宿，預計同一時間可服務約300人 |url=https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/489638 |website=Fortune Insight |date=2020-04-16 |accessdate=2020-04-28 |archive-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416085254/https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/489638 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。鄭志雯為現任[[香港中文大學|香港中文大學]]酒店旅遊管理學院顧問委員會主席<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/governance/committee/english/hotel.html|title=CUHK > Advisory Boards and Committees > Advisory Committee on Hotel and Tourism Management|website=The Chinese University of Hong Kong|access-date=2020-03-11|archive-date=2020-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105121154/http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/governance/committee/english/hotel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾任[[香港理工大學|香港理工大學]]酒店旅遊業管理學院業界顧問委員會委員（2014年-2020年）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polyu.edu.hk/htm/download/Advisory_Committees_SHTM.pdf|title=The Hong Kong Polytechnic University School of Hotel and Tourism Management Membership List of School Advisory Committee|access-date=2020-03-11|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420214748/http://www.polyu.edu.hk/htm/download/Advisory_Committees_SHTM.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

